                    </div>
                    <span>This is a well-written book on an interesting subject.  The author keeps the subject moving by the way he has the book organized.  It follows in the path by which a slave went from one plantation to the slave market in New Orleans to a new plantation in the Lower South.  I enjoyed reading the narrative.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">very informative and specific</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
